---
title: Double Bacon, Apple and Cheddar Melts with BBQ Potato Rounds and Honey-Mustard Dipper
description: Here's bacon melt that'll sure be a hit with the whole family! Sweet apples help to cut some of the richness from the bacon and cheese and the BBQ-spiced potatoes get a honey mustard mayo as a dunking buddy!
